criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with systemic sclerosis according to the 2013 ACR/EULAR classification
             criteria for SSc;

          -  Patients with gastrointestinal symptoms related to SSc including: gastrointestinal
             reflux, bloating, diarrhea and constipation;

          -  Written informed consent provided by the subjects.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Overlap syndromes with systemic lupus erythematosus, polymyositis/dermatomyositis and
             rheumatoid arthritis;

          -  Use of antibiotics and/or probiotics four weeks before baseline;
